{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"97byquf304s345mp9uuoqh2","title":"GitHub Analyze","desc":"","updated":1664735789404,"created":1664272636038,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.rust.projects.github-analyze","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"7822bed03dd05c97b73cf28b0844fecb","links":[],"anchors":{"github-analyze":{"type":"header","text":"Github Analyze","value":"github-analyze","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"why":{"type":"header","text":"Why?","value":"why","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"how":{"type":"header","text":"How?","value":"how","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"todo":{"type":"header","text":"Todo","value":"todo","line":25,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"k4tajydmoc1vf0cuok1ckjq","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"github-analyze\">GitHub Analyze<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#github-analyze\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"github-analyze-1\">Github Analyze<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#github-analyze-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"why\">Why?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#why\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Need to analyze github PRs &#x26; commits in a range of time</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"how\">How?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#how\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Authorize Github request\n<ul>\n<li>Use <code>Authorization: Bearer &#x3C;Token></code> </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Get github information in a time range\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/rest/commits/commits#list-commits\">https://docs.github.com/en/rest/commits/commits#list-commits</a></li>\n<li>per owner, per repo => need to list repos &#x26; owners </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>List all Pull request\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/rest/pulls/pulls#list-pull-requests\">https://docs.github.com/en/rest/pulls/pulls#list-pull-requests</a></li>\n<li>per owner, per repo => config</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Todo<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#todo\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a HTTP client\n<ul>\n<li>basic client: <a href=\"https://hyper.rs/guides/client/basic/\">https://hyper.rs/guides/client/basic/</a></li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](https://wiki.dendron.so/)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"alwaysPrompt","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNo